title: 01/24/22 DPS Hour 3 Evan McPherson and Carson Palmer
itunes:title: 01/24/22 DPS Hour 3 Evan McPherson and Carson Palmer
description:
Evan McPherson Talks to Dan about what it was like to kick the game winning field goal. Carson Palmer tells Dan that he thinks that Tom Brady will be back in Tampa and says that Aaron Rodgers will not be back in Green Bay.
